<p>
  The president and legal representative of the Mountainboarding Association, Rolando Chinchilla Dinarte, was grateful
  to all the collaborators, especially Jeroen De Booser, Rebeca Quesadas Cespedez, Alejandra Montoya Picado and
  Cristopher Arce Robles, for their contributions during the event.
</p>
<p>
  The attendees were rewarded for the show that the participants made and the association hopes to be able to continue
  holding these types of events with the support of other organizations.
</p>
<p>
  The results of the first places are summarized in the following tables for each modality and category.
</p>

